Prints the config object to STDOUT

Source: R/Config.R
show-tiledb_config-method.Rd

Prints the config object to STDOUT

Usage

# S4 method for class 'tiledb_config'
show(object)

Arguments

object

tiledb_config object

Examples

cfg <- tiledb_config()
show(cfg)
